22:32.070 --> 22:35.474
As you think about your detractors, who might they be?

22:36.226 --> 22:39.491
and what would it look like for you to leave them in God's hands?

22:56.875 --> 23:00.820
Would you be reminded like Joseph what they intend for evil?

23:00.920 --> 23:02.162
God can work for good.

23:05.218 --> 23:09.244
to leave vengeance in the hands of the Lord for it is his.

23:11.487 --> 23:15.252
None of us are an impartial judge.

23:22.502 --> 23:28.851
Maybe for you this morning, the application is to shoot a text to the people in your life that you've alienated.

23:30.293 --> 23:34.098
Maybe it's recommitting

23:34.306 --> 23:40.614
to joining a small group this year or showing up to church because you've been out for too long.

23:52.488 --> 23:55.252
Lord, as the old hymn writer said, our hearts are prone to wonder.

23:55.993 --> 23:56.593
We can feel it.

23:57.675 --> 24:03.602
Would you take our hearts and seal them, seal them for your courts above?

24:03.842 --> 24:09.088
We thank you that you're a God who speaks through your word and to our individual hearts.

24:10.089 --> 24:17.257
And we're thankful that you've called us into a great work of advancing your kingdom to the ends of the earth.

24:18.198 --> 24:24.945
That you would use humble jars of clay like us is really wild.

24:25.646 --> 24:33.074
And so we pray we would be vessels available for use and moldable in the potter's hands.

24:33.538 --> 24:37.023
for the individuals here and also the ones watching online.

24:37.965 --> 24:51.986
I pray Holy Spirit that you would take your word and bring it to bear in very specific ways and bring conviction so that our response is one of humility and obedience.

24:52.006 --> 24:54.190
Lord, we surrender to you our plans.

24:54.490 --> 25:02.162
We surrender the opposition to those plans and we recommit ourselves to the big

25:02.434 --> 25:28.786
why, the big answer why, of why you're calling us to do what you've put before us and whether that's raising children or grandchildren or starting a new venture or creative project, we pray that you would take your word this morning and strengthen us by your grace.

25:29.186 --> 25:42.073
so that we would not grow weary in doing the good thing you've called us to, but that we would keep persevering and receive the reward because we kept working and keep pushing and decided not to give up.

25:42.093 --> 25:46.121
And we pray these things in Jesus' name, and God's people said, Amen.

